[list]&#xD;
[*] Copy your personal verification code shown below into your clickboard or write it down on a paper.&#xD;
[*] After that please start Florensia, select your character you want to verify and jump into the game.&#xD;
[*] After you joined the server whipser the code to yourself by using the chatbox.&#xD;
[*] Take a screenshot which should be automatically saved to your Florensia folder (.../Florensia/Bin/Capture)&#xD;
[*] Do not resize, cut or rework your screenshot in any other ways.&#xD;
[*] Reopen this page and upload your [b]original[/b] screenshot. It will be verified by a moderator who will grand or deny your request afterwards.&#xD;
